VERSION 1
WHEN PRESENT (?i)^[^#]*\.\s*(raw|extra)\s*\(\s*
WHEN EXPR PRESENT:(request|params|query|format\(|f\"|f'|\+) && MISSING:(params=|placeholders|bindparam)
REPORT AS area_of_interest
REASON Detects insecure SQL queries using the "raw" and "extra" methods in Python.
TRACE Externalized rule logic for Insecure SQL Queries: raw and extra.
